{"markdown":{"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"::: {.question}\n\n**Timing of Equity Issuance Under Asymmetric Information**\n\n```{r}\n#| eval: true\n#| results: asis\n#| echo: false\n#| warning: false\n\nset.seed(908)\nlibrary(webexercises)\nlibrary(knitr)\n\ntrue_value_today  <- round(rnorm(1, mean = 210, sd = 6), 2)\ntrue_value_future <- true_value_today + round(rnorm(1, mean = 25, sd = 5), 2)\n\nmarket_belief_today  <- round(true_value_today - runif(1, 15, 40), 2)\nmarket_belief_future <- round(true_value_future - runif(1, 10, 25), 2)\n\nshares <- round(rnorm(1, mean = 12, sd = 1), 2)\n\nprice_today  <- round(market_belief_today  / shares, 2)\nprice_future <- round(market_belief_future / shares, 2)\n\ncapital_needed <- round(rnorm(1, mean = 30, sd = 3), 2)\n\nshares_today  <- round(capital_needed / price_today, 2)\nshares_future <- round(capital_needed / price_future, 2)\n```\n\nA firm currently has `r shares`M shares. True firm value today is `r true_value_today`M, but the market believes it is only `r market_belief_today`M. In six months, the true value will be `r true_value_future`M, but markets will believe it is `r market_belief_future`M.\n\nThe firm needs to raise `r capital_needed`M and is considering issuing equity today or in six months.\n\nCompute:\n\n(a) share price today\n\n(b) share price in six months\n\n(c) shares issued today\n\n(d) shares issued in six months\n\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;\"> <label for=\"module9_num_q8a_single\"><strong>a. Price today ($):</strong></label> <input type=\"number\" id=\"module9_num_q8a_single\" name=\"module9_num_q8a_single\" style=\"width:160px;\" data-correct-answer=`r price_today` data-tolerance=\"0.5\" step=\"0.01\" /> </form> <div id=\"feedback-module9_num_q8a_single\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\"> ✅ Price today = Market belief / shares = `r market_belief_today` / `r shares` = <b>`r price_today`</b>. </div> \n:::\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;\"> <label for=\"module9_num_q8b_single\"><strong>b. Price in six months ($):</strong></label> <input type=\"number\" id=\"module9_num_q8b_single\" name=\"module9_num_q8b_single\" style=\"width:160px;\" data-correct-answer=`r price_future` data-tolerance=\"0.5\" step=\"0.01\" /> </form> <div id=\"feedback-module9_num_q8b_single\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\"> ✅ Price future = Market belief future / shares = `r market_belief_future` / `r shares` = <b>`r price_future`</b>. </div> \n:::\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;\"> <label for=\"module9_num_q8c_single\"><strong>c. Shares issued today (millions):</strong></label> <input type=\"number\" id=\"module9_num_q8c_single\" name=\"module9_num_q8c_single\" style=\"width:160px;\" data-correct-answer=`r shares_today` data-tolerance=\"0.1\" step=\"0.01\" /> </form> <div id=\"feedback-module9_num_q8c_single\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\"> ✅ Shares today = `r capital_needed` / `r price_today` = <b>`r shares_today`M</b>. </div> \n:::\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;\"> <label for=\"module9_num_q8d_single\"><strong>d. Shares issued in six months (millions):</strong></label> <input type=\"number\" id=\"module9_num_q8d_single\" name=\"module9_num_q8d_single\" style=\"width:160px;\" data-correct-answer=`r shares_future` data-tolerance=\"0.1\" step=\"0.01\" /> </form> <div id=\"feedback-module9_num_q8d_single\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\"> ✅ Shares future = `r capital_needed` / `r price_future` = <b>`r shares_future`M</b>. </div> \n:::\n:::","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-for